  "title": "Piquant Kenyan Lamb Tagine",
  "description": "A flavorful and aromatic Kenyan lamb dish cooked in a traditional clay tagine, featuring a blend of spices and red chilli, with a garlicky and slightly sweet flavor profile, suitable for serving at a Buddhist temple gathering.",
